psalm.text:
[[Ps 60,3]]O God, you have rejected us and broken our defenses;
You have been angry; rally us!

[[Ps 60,4]]You have rocked the country and split it open; 
repair the cracks in it, for it is tottering.
[[Ps 60,5]]You have made your people feel hardships; 
you have given us stupefying wine.

[[Ps 60,12]]Have not you, O God, rejected us, 
so that you go not forth, O God, with our armies?
[[Ps 60,13]]Give us aid against the foe, 
for worthless is the help of men.
